snippet.textDisplay: I'm surprised! I didn't even know such a song existed in our culture. Great concept by CokeStudio. This type of work is a great way to preserve this type of old but golden songs in our culture. These diamonds are going extinct due to modernization. I personally mostly listen to modern bands. But this song gave me goosebumps. What a composition and melody. Great way to make these attractive to the youth listeners and make these songs live.❤❤❤
